{"word":"G3882 - παράλιος - parálios - par-al'-ee-os - Sea coast","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">παράλιος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">parálios</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">par-al'-ee-os</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Sea coast</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"கடலோரத்திலிருக்கிற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"by the sea, maritime"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G3844 - παρά - pará - par-ah'/3844\">G3844</a> and <a href=\"#/G251 - ἅλς - háls - halce/251\">G251</a>; <i>beside</i> the <i>salt</i> (sea), that is, <i>maritime:</i> - sea coast.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}